# Playable Song - Camera Controller

The Camera Controller controls everything about the camera.

## Properties

- <b>Pivot Position</b> <i>(Storyboardable, Vector3)</i>: The position of the camera pivot in the
game space.

- <b>Pivot Distance</b> <i>(Storyboardable, Float)</i>: How far the actual camera is to the pivot.

- <b>Pivot Rotation</b> <i>(Storyboardable, Vector3)</i>: The rotation of the camera pivot.